text: Great place for children of all ages to learn more about molecular biology skills! The educators are very friendly and passionate too, my children enjoy themselves a lot! Highly recommend to parents! :)
Came across their lesson post on FB, signed my DD and friends up for their June Holiday programmes and they had fun! The instructors are very sweet too!
Been this the genetics programme and had lots of hands on opportunities! Thank you for such a great learning opportunity!
